  <summary date="2017-04-05T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Better Drive Act

This bill repeals provisions requiring the Department of Transportation to withhold a certain amount of a state's apportionment of federal-aid highway funds if the state fails to enact and enforce a law that requires the revocation or suspension of drivers' licenses of individuals convicted of drug offenses.</summary>
